T02D3350:34b-1: bhri ku t'i s'a dha nam /
T02D3350:34b-3: khro gnyer can gyi sgrub pa'i thabs /

T02D3350:34b-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas rang gi snying gar
T02D3350:34b-6: zla ba'i dbus su sa bon drug pa'i bzhi pa

T02D3350:35a-1: mnan cing zla phyed kyis dbu brgyan pa'o //

T02D3350:35a-9: lhag ma so sor byas pa ni rdo rje'i mtshan nyid do //
T02D3350:35a-10: 'di ni khro gnyer can gyi phyag rgya'o //
T02D3350:35a-11: phyi nas sngags bzlas par bya ste /
